1
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:55,000
[A Dream Within A Dream]

2
00:01:55,030 --> 00:01:58,020
[Episode 20]

3
00:01:58,070 --> 00:02:02,330
[Song Residence]

4
00:02:07,310 --> 00:02:08,440
How come it's you?

5
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,630
Miss Song Yiting, you gave me
such generous gifts.

6
00:02:15,630 --> 00:02:16,910
How could I not come?

7
00:02:17,710 --> 00:02:19,630
I want to see Li Shiliu.

8
00:02:20,870 --> 00:02:22,360
Chief is extremely busy,

9
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:24,380
so he assigned this matter to me.

10
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:26,630
Miss Yiting, feel free
to make any requests.

11
00:02:26,630 --> 00:02:27,470
I'll certainly comply.

12
00:02:27,470 --> 00:02:28,530
Don't call me that.

13
00:02:28,910 --> 00:02:29,710
And also,

14
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,530
keep your distance.

15
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,760
Let me be honest with you.

16
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,960
Today, only Li Shiliu

17
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,560
can take what I have in my possession.

18
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:44,360
That's a bit unreasonable, isn't it?

19
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:46,190
That belongs to Waning River Crescent.

20
00:02:46,190 --> 00:02:46,910
Is that so?

21
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:50,180
It belongs to Waning River Crescent?

22
00:02:53,030 --> 00:02:53,840
Either

23
00:02:54,310 --> 00:02:56,030
you let me see Li Shiliu today,

24
00:02:57,079 --> 00:02:57,870
or

25
00:02:58,630 --> 00:03:00,310
Mr. Chu from the
capital prefecture's office

26
00:03:00,310 --> 00:03:02,110
would be very interested to know

27
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,470
how his precious sword

28
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,240
ended up in your hands.

29
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,560
I bathed myself and put on perfume

30
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,310
only to encounter such filth.

31
00:03:10,470 --> 00:03:11,560
What rotten luck.

32
00:03:18,020 --> 00:03:18,340
[Noon]

33
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:18,990
[Early Afternoon]

34
00:03:19,010 --> 00:03:19,720
[Late Afternoon]

35
00:03:19,760 --> 00:03:21,410
[Evening]

36
00:03:22,590 --> 00:03:24,050
I can't take this anymore.

37
00:03:24,190 --> 00:03:25,150
An official's daughter

38
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:27,030
dares to double-cross the Nightwalkers.

39
00:03:27,030 --> 00:03:28,360
I'm going to
take that sword back right now.

40
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,590
I'll take all the blame
if anything goes wrong.

41
00:03:29,590 --> 00:03:31,000
Can you calm down?

42
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,000
You think the Song Residence is some gang

43
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:32,840
you can just barge into?

44
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,870
Listen.

45
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,280
When dealing with officials' families,

46
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,710
we need to follow proper protocol.

47
00:03:36,710 --> 00:03:38,280
Then what do you suggest we do?

48
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,800
If we don't get that sword back,

49
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,800
we can't hide it from Chief anymore.

50
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,590
Bring me my battle robe.

51
00:03:47,150 --> 00:03:48,400
At critical moments,

52
00:03:49,310 --> 00:03:51,240
I'm still the one who has to step in.

53
00:04:09,030 --> 00:04:09,840
Thank you,

54
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,080
Miss Song Yiting.

55
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,870
Mr. Li, why so formal?

56
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,560
Just call me Yiting.

57
00:04:17,230 --> 00:04:18,160
Miss Yiting, feel free...

58
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,220
Don't call me that.

59
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,730
Keep your distance.

60
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,830
My Lady, what exactly would it take

61
00:04:25,830 --> 00:04:27,230
for you to return

62
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,890
what you've stolen from me?

63
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,630
How can you call it stealing?

64
00:04:30,630 --> 00:04:31,830
That sounds so harsh.

65
00:04:32,070 --> 00:04:34,630
I gifted you 73 paintings

66
00:04:34,750 --> 00:04:35,560
and merely took

67
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:37,830
a small token in return.

68
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,750
If you're so attached to it,

69
00:04:39,750 --> 00:04:41,630
perhaps we could arrange a trade?

70
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,800
Offering yourself in marriage is
certainly out of the question.

71
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:51,360
The Waning River Crescent doesn't engage
in such transactions.

72
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,630
You jest, Mr. Li.

73
00:04:52,870 --> 00:04:54,159
It's not that serious.

74
00:04:54,830 --> 00:04:57,000
I only ask for three days.

75
00:04:57,750 --> 00:04:58,920
You need three days?

76
00:05:03,630 --> 00:05:04,760
You misunderstand.

77
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:06,680
You were right before.

78
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:09,360
I have no experience
with the martial arts world,

79
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:11,240
and you don't understand
noble family customs.

80
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:13,360
Our backgrounds are worlds apart,

81
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:15,930
so this relationship may not be suitable.

82
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:20,560
But if we don't even give
each other a chance,

83
00:05:21,070 --> 00:05:24,000
then there's definitely
no possibility of a future.

84
00:05:24,710 --> 00:05:27,150
How do you propose we try?

85
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,240
Let's spend three days together

86
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:31,100
to get to know each other's lives.

87
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:33,070
If after three days,

88
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:35,000
you still feel nothing for me,

89
00:05:35,270 --> 00:05:36,720
I'll return the sword.

90
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:38,750
But if you do fall for me,

91
00:05:39,430 --> 00:05:41,550
then you must ask my parents for my hand.

92
00:05:41,550 --> 00:05:42,580
For your hand?

93
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,310
Playing for such high stakes?

94
00:05:43,870 --> 00:05:47,159
♪ Clap once, we ride together
in the bridal sedan ♪

95
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:47,560
You've experienced all sorts of things.

96
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:49,360
Surely this small request

97
00:05:48,070 --> 00:05:51,510
♪ Clap twice,
the Song family's rocket shoots high ♪

98
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:51,610
doesn't frighten you, right?

99
00:05:52,170 --> 00:05:53,180
♪ Riding in the bridal sedan ♪

100
00:05:53,740 --> 00:05:54,740
♪ Riding in the bridal sedan ♪

101
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,730
♪ The bridal sedan is fabulous ♪

102
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:16,750
Rather than handing over Miss Song Yiting

103
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:18,600
to strengthen someone else's power,

104
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:21,190
why don't you marry both sisters?

105
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,950
Marry a virtuous wife

106
00:06:23,750 --> 00:06:25,350
and have a pretty concubine.

107
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:29,130
Firmly grasp the Song family's influence
in your hands.

108
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,680
My answer

109
00:06:32,070 --> 00:06:33,270
is still the same.

110
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,240
Very well.

111
00:06:40,870 --> 00:06:42,070
Nan Heng clearly has

112
00:06:42,070 --> 00:06:43,950
the idea of us sisters marrying
one husband.

113
00:06:43,950 --> 00:06:45,690
Is there no way to avoid

114
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:48,100
these iconic scenes from the script?

115
00:07:04,430 --> 00:07:06,230
The palace is full of treachery.

116
00:07:06,340 --> 00:07:08,140
One must be careful everywhere.

117
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:09,510
Even if you don't harm others,

118
00:07:09,510 --> 00:07:11,830
you must guard against others harming you.

119
00:07:11,830 --> 00:07:13,510
He may not want to kill me,

120
00:07:14,070 --> 00:07:16,270
but I will certainly die because of him.

121
00:07:16,630 --> 00:07:17,510
These are the rules.

122
00:07:17,510 --> 00:07:18,390
It's destined.

123
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:19,950
Then, break the rules.

124
00:07:19,950 --> 00:07:21,410
Destroy what's destined.

125
00:07:25,830 --> 00:07:26,630
No.

126
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:29,160
At least I can survive until
the second-to-last episode.

127
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,830
But if Song Yiting is deceived by him,

128
00:07:30,830 --> 00:07:32,600
that's a lifetime matter.

129
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:35,390
I must defy fate.

130
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:37,560
Nan Heng,

131
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:39,070
I'm sorry.

132
00:07:47,750 --> 00:07:48,680
My Lady.

133
00:07:49,310 --> 00:07:50,250
My Lady,

134
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:51,480
how could you do

135
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,240
such labor yourself?

136
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,370
Let me do it instead,

137
00:07:54,430 --> 00:07:55,960
so you won't hurt yourself.

138
00:07:56,830 --> 00:07:57,720
Yimeng,

139
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:59,920
I heard that after
the ladies left that day,

140
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:01,720
you had quite a talk with Heng.

141
00:08:02,190 --> 00:08:03,800
Have you changed your mind?

142
00:08:04,390 --> 00:08:05,190
My Lady,

143
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,680
I was foolish before.

144
00:08:07,750 --> 00:08:09,360
The Seventh Prince is
such a wonderful person,

145
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,950
and I failed to cherish him.

146
00:08:11,390 --> 00:08:12,360
Thanks to you

147
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,760
for never giving up on me,

148
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,660
I now have the chance to marry him.

149
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,510
It's just...

150
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:20,920
What's wrong?

151
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:23,120
Has Heng mistreated you?

152
00:08:24,710 --> 00:08:25,700
No,

153
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,000
His Highness hasn't mistreated me.

154
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:29,800
My Lady,

155
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:32,049
after meeting those noble ladies,

156
00:08:32,110 --> 00:08:34,110
he started ignoring me completely.

157
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:35,789
I followed your instructions

158
00:08:35,789 --> 00:08:37,390
and gave him those pastries,

159
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:39,080
but after taking them,

160
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,480
he just turned and left,

161
00:08:41,549 --> 00:08:44,430
without saying a single kind word to me.

162
00:08:45,390 --> 00:08:46,720
I'm worried

163
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:48,910
that he might've taken a fancy to
one of those noble ladies

164
00:08:48,910 --> 00:08:51,040
and is thinking of taking a concubine.

165
00:08:51,140 --> 00:08:52,400
That's impossible.

166
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,840
Those ladies that day

167
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:56,620
were all terrified by Heng.

168
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:59,870
In this capital, the only woman
with such courage

169
00:09:00,390 --> 00:09:01,790
is you, Yimeng.

170
00:09:02,780 --> 00:09:04,110
Thank you, My Lady.

171
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:07,080
That's what I've been telling myself too.

172
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:07,870
But...

173
00:09:08,790 --> 00:09:11,480
But as long as I'm not by his side,

174
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:13,840
I can neither eat nor sleep properly.

175
00:09:14,510 --> 00:09:15,550
I'm afraid

176
00:09:15,750 --> 00:09:17,540
that I might pass away

177
00:09:17,630 --> 00:09:19,670
before our wedding day arrives.

178
00:09:20,790 --> 00:09:21,600
Yimeng.

179
00:09:24,390 --> 00:09:25,200
Yimeng.

180
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,380
Yimeng!

181
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:30,310
Yimeng!

182
00:09:34,910 --> 00:09:35,720
Quick!

183
00:09:35,870 --> 00:09:36,790
Quickly call the imperial physician!

184
00:09:36,790 --> 00:09:37,120
Yes,

185
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:37,720
My Lady.

186
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,150
All illnesses can be cured,

187
00:09:40,150 --> 00:09:41,550
but lovesickness has no remedy.

188
00:09:41,550 --> 00:09:42,320
My Lady,

189
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,510
I beg you.

190
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,960
Please let me go to the Prince's residence

191
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,360
to be with the Seventh Prince,

192
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,120
would you?

193
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,350
Good child,

194
00:09:50,390 --> 00:09:51,900
I promise you.

195
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:54,150
I'll grant you anything you wish.

196
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,720
Thank you, My Lady.

197
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:01,480
My Lady,

198
00:10:01,910 --> 00:10:03,510
your acting was terrible.

199
00:10:03,510 --> 00:10:05,200
Why don't you learn from me sometime?

200
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,670
You have the nerve to say that?

201
00:10:06,670 --> 00:10:08,390
You put chili sauce in there.

202
00:10:08,390 --> 00:10:10,240
I wonder if she noticed.

203
00:10:11,150 --> 00:10:12,320
Whatever.

204
00:10:12,630 --> 00:10:13,960
Both of you, listen carefully.

205
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,030
From now on,

206
00:10:15,030 --> 00:10:16,000
I'll keep a close eye

207
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:16,750
on Nan Heng.

208
00:10:16,750 --> 00:10:17,510
You two

209
00:10:17,510 --> 00:10:19,040
watch Song Yiting closely.

210
00:10:22,790 --> 00:10:24,860
Yimeng is so desperate

211
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,700
to leave the palace and see Heng

212
00:10:26,790 --> 00:10:29,120
that she'd go to such lengths.

213
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:31,030
Miss Song has gone to great trouble.

214
00:10:31,030 --> 00:10:34,600
She must be deeply in love
with His Highness.

215
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,910
Love grows deeply,

216
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,840
blossoms, and bears fruits.

217
00:10:38,870 --> 00:10:40,400
They'll have many children

218
00:10:40,460 --> 00:10:41,960
and many generations!

219
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:52,600
So you

220
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:55,170
took the initiative to tell Mother

221
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:56,960
to come

222
00:10:57,670 --> 00:10:59,030
and serve me?

223
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:04,440
Your Highness is busy.

224
00:11:04,910 --> 00:11:06,910
Since I'm about to become your wife,

225
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:09,000
I need to learn

226
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:11,510
how to serve you well.

227
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:14,750
Then in the future,

228
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:18,980
I can pass down your genes,

229
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,550
blossom and bear fruit,

230
00:11:20,550 --> 00:11:22,120
and have many children

231
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:23,480
and generations.

232
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:23,840
Got it.

233
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:24,670
Then...

234
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,080
You may leave.

235
00:11:32,620 --> 00:11:34,900
Did I do something wrong?

236
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:36,510
Or Your Highness,

237
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:39,480
do you not want to see me at all?

238
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,120
Fine.

239
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:47,790
If you are well,

240
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:49,320
everything is great.

241
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:52,350
I'll leave now.

242
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,240
From now on,

243
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:57,240
I won't disturb your life anymore.

244
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:07,630
I'm really leaving.

245
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:18,090
You said you cared about me.

246
00:12:18,510 --> 00:12:21,600
You said you wanted to
protect me forever.

247
00:12:22,630 --> 00:12:24,210
People change easily,

248
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,840
but love is hard to break.

249
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:28,810
What a pity for my sincerity.

250
00:12:29,150 --> 00:12:31,550
I loved the wrong person.

251
00:12:31,630 --> 00:12:32,710
Come back.

252
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,860
What's wrong, Your Highness?

253
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,410
Your acting is not good.

254
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:46,960
Don't act next time.

255
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,260
However,

256
00:12:49,790 --> 00:12:51,550
since you've already spoken
with Mother,

257
00:12:51,550 --> 00:12:53,440
you should stay here in the residence.

258
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:55,300
It's not safe outside these days.

259
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,120
Don't go out

260
00:12:56,910 --> 00:12:58,320
and cause me trouble,

261
00:12:58,960 --> 00:12:59,750
understand?

262
00:13:01,210 --> 00:13:02,990
I got it.

263
00:13:03,150 --> 00:13:05,480
Your Highness is truly

264
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:07,080
the best fiancé in the world.

265
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:09,370
I'll go settle in now.

266
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:56,300
Your Highness,

267
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:57,930
what are you looking at?

268
00:13:58,630 --> 00:14:00,630
What's so interesting about hands?

269
00:14:02,910 --> 00:14:03,720
What is it?

270
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:05,720
Chancellor Gao has brought his advisors

271
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:06,790
to discuss state affairs with you.

272
00:14:06,790 --> 00:14:08,650
They're waiting in the main hall.

273
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:11,390
Got it.

274
00:14:12,510 --> 00:14:13,370
Your Highness,

275
00:14:13,550 --> 00:14:16,030
Chu Guihong just came to steal something,

276
00:14:16,230 --> 00:14:18,150
and now Miss Song comes to stay.

277
00:14:18,150 --> 00:14:19,600
What's going on here?

278
00:14:20,550 --> 00:14:22,950
She says she's here to
serve me personally,

279
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:25,800
but there's not a word of truth
in what she says.

280
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,120
Keep an eye on her.

281
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:30,100
If she needs anything,

282
00:14:30,270 --> 00:14:32,200
make sure it's properly arranged.

283
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:33,030
But Your Highness,

284
00:14:33,030 --> 00:14:35,230
your instructions are contradictory.

285
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:36,750
Should I be guarding against her

286
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:38,080
or taking care of her?

287
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:44,080
