00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:08,680
I want something that

577
00:30:08,750 --> 00:30:10,830
makes someone abstain from women,

578
00:30:10,830 --> 00:30:11,880
purifies their mind, and reduces desires,

579
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:15,680
preferably something that would make them
become a monk on the spot.

580
00:30:17,030 --> 00:30:20,980
[Song Residence]

581
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:23,790
Shangguan,

582
00:30:24,270 --> 00:30:26,330
Miss Song Yiting is about to come out.

583
00:30:26,790 --> 00:30:28,270
Before you put on your battle robe,

584
00:30:28,270 --> 00:30:30,640
please repeat today's mission once more.

585
00:30:32,070 --> 00:30:32,880
Alright.

586
00:30:34,440 --> 00:30:36,240
Combining our Chief's arrogance,

587
00:30:36,240 --> 00:30:37,610
Nan Rui's ignorance,

588
00:30:37,790 --> 00:30:39,970
and Chu Guihong's dullness,

589
00:30:40,270 --> 00:30:43,200
I vow to be the most detestable man
in Great Jing.

590
00:30:43,550 --> 00:30:45,400
I will surely destroy

591
00:30:46,590 --> 00:30:48,190
Miss Song's feelings for me.

592
00:30:49,070 --> 00:30:51,130
Everything depends on this one move.

593
00:30:57,380 --> 00:30:59,170
♪ Oh my, baby ♪

594
00:30:59,750 --> 00:31:02,130
♪ What earrings do you like this time? ♪

595
00:31:00,250 --> 00:31:01,900
[400 copper coins]

596
00:31:01,350 --> 00:31:02,310
So expensive.

597
00:31:02,720 --> 00:31:04,440
♪ Such expensive earrings are puzzling ♪

598
00:31:04,690 --> 00:31:07,500
♪ Do they think it rains money? ♪

599
00:31:06,180 --> 00:31:07,900
[Jewelry]

600
00:31:08,220 --> 00:31:10,250
♪ It rains money ♪

601
00:31:10,110 --> 00:31:11,400
So ugly.

602
00:31:10,930 --> 00:31:13,060
♪ Sploosh, splash ♪

603
00:31:13,710 --> 00:31:15,890
♪ It rains money ♪

604
00:31:16,530 --> 00:31:18,330
♪ I'm getting rich, I'm getting rich ♪

605
00:31:56,140 --> 00:31:58,230
[Jewelry Shop]

606
00:31:58,350 --> 00:31:59,490
Why are you

607
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:00,900
holding the packages?

608
00:32:01,070 --> 00:32:01,960
Oh, right.

609
00:32:03,250 --> 00:32:09,330
[Candle Shop]

610
00:32:31,720 --> 00:32:32,720
Does it look nice?

611
00:32:33,070 --> 00:32:36,110
I want to wear this tomorrow
when I meet my friends.

612
00:32:37,030 --> 00:32:37,830
It's ugly.

613
00:32:39,480 --> 00:32:40,680
Extremely ugly.

614
00:32:41,270 --> 00:32:43,600
You're wearing this to meet your friends?

615
00:32:44,640 --> 00:32:47,570
People might think you're
trying to seduce someone.

616
00:32:53,030 --> 00:32:55,200
And you call yourself a noble lady?

617
00:32:56,830 --> 00:32:58,050
In my opinion,

618
00:32:58,720 --> 00:33:00,990
you're nothing but a vulgar woman

619
00:33:01,070 --> 00:33:03,160
who tries to win over men.

620
00:33:18,270 --> 00:33:18,960
What else do you need to buy?

621
00:33:18,960 --> 00:33:20,070
Can you hurry up?

622
00:33:20,480 --> 00:33:22,810
Waning River Crescent has a meeting soon.

623
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:27,650
A successful man like myself

624
00:33:27,830 --> 00:33:28,680
simply doesn't have time

625
00:33:28,680 --> 00:33:30,830
to waste on such shallow matters.

626
00:33:30,920 --> 00:33:31,720
Enough.

627
00:33:33,640 --> 00:33:34,720
If your goal

628
00:33:35,160 --> 00:33:36,560
is to make me dislike you,

629
00:33:37,030 --> 00:33:38,240
then congratulations.

630
00:33:38,240 --> 00:33:39,300
You've succeeded.

631
00:33:42,000 --> 00:33:44,260
Don't bother accompanying me tomorrow.

632
00:34:04,480 --> 00:34:06,440
Besides the one Miss Song Yiting
is wearing,

633
00:34:06,440 --> 00:34:08,280
this one is for you.

634
00:34:09,110 --> 00:34:10,110
For me?

635
00:34:12,670 --> 00:34:16,420
[Half a month ago]

636
00:34:16,480 --> 00:34:18,940
The men's and women's outfits
really match!

637
00:34:19,480 --> 00:34:21,840
Mr. Li is a person of integrity.

638
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:24,880
This blue color suits him perfectly.

639
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:27,920
He often engages in martial arts contests,

640
00:34:27,920 --> 00:34:29,510
so his clothes can't just look good.

641
00:34:29,510 --> 00:34:30,670
They must also be durable

642
00:34:30,670 --> 00:34:31,670
and lightweight.

643
00:34:32,230 --> 00:34:34,670
Areas that touch the skin,
like the cuffs and collars,

644
00:34:34,670 --> 00:34:36,130
must be crafted with care.

645
00:34:38,070 --> 00:34:38,880
Madam,

646
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:41,840
I need your help with something.

647
00:34:42,670 --> 00:34:43,650
Go ahead.

648
00:34:44,190 --> 00:34:46,860
Mr. Li has a condition on his face

649
00:34:46,960 --> 00:34:49,090
and doesn't show his true appearance.

650
00:34:49,510 --> 00:34:50,639
But I believe

651
00:34:50,760 --> 00:34:53,070
he is the most handsome man in the world.

652
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:55,400
Only the most vivid mask

653
00:34:55,840 --> 00:34:57,100
would be worthy of him.

654
00:34:59,190 --> 00:35:00,510
These are my designs.

655
00:35:03,050 --> 00:35:04,110
Take it!

656
00:35:04,800 --> 00:35:07,030
I've run this tailor shop for many years,

657
00:35:07,030 --> 00:35:09,000
and Miss Song Yiting is
a regular customer,

658
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:11,710
but I've never seen her care
so much about someone.

659
00:35:11,710 --> 00:35:12,920
Such fine things

660
00:35:12,920 --> 00:35:14,630
are wasted on someone like you.

661
00:35:14,630 --> 00:35:15,230
Pah!

662
00:35:15,400 --> 00:35:16,730
I don't want your money.

663
00:35:27,890 --> 00:35:31,950
[Righteousness and Virtue]

664
00:35:51,000 --> 00:35:52,180
This is...

665
00:35:54,230 --> 00:35:55,030
A tonic?

666
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:57,280
Miss Song,

667
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:58,260
isn't this bowl

668
00:35:58,340 --> 00:36:00,140
a bit too large?

669
00:36:00,230 --> 00:36:01,540
I came here

670
00:36:01,760 --> 00:36:03,550
specifically to take care of

671
00:36:03,550 --> 00:36:04,550
His Highness's health.

672
00:36:04,550 --> 00:36:06,110
Without some strong medicine,

673
00:36:06,110 --> 00:36:07,840
how can I properly nourish him?

674
00:36:08,440 --> 00:36:09,360
Your Highness,

675
00:36:09,630 --> 00:36:11,360
please drink it while it's hot.

676
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:12,360
If it gets cold,

677
00:36:12,800 --> 00:36:15,000
the medicinal effects won't be as good.

678
00:36:16,550 --> 00:36:17,510
Drink up now.

679
00:36:20,510 --> 00:36:23,240
So what exactly are the effects
of this medicine?

680
00:36:24,590 --> 00:36:25,850
It nourishes

681
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:28,230
the heart, liver, spleen,
lungs, and kidneys—

682
00:36:28,230 --> 00:36:29,110
everything.

683
00:36:29,280 --> 00:36:30,960
It's good for your health.

684
00:36:30,960 --> 00:36:31,710
Drink it quickly.

685
00:36:31,710 --> 00:36:33,910
Are you trying to make him plump like me?

686
00:36:35,400 --> 00:36:36,400
You're too young.

687
00:36:36,400 --> 00:36:37,660
You don't understand.

688
00:36:38,480 --> 00:36:40,080
I don't think this is a tonic.

689
00:36:40,550 --> 00:36:42,750
You're trying to poison me, aren't you?

690
00:36:43,190 --> 00:36:44,000
I...

691
00:36:45,760 --> 00:36:46,680
Your Highness,

692
00:36:47,030 --> 00:36:49,670
for the sake of my future happiness,

693
00:36:50,070 --> 00:36:52,020
I certainly wouldn't harm you.

694
00:36:56,880 --> 00:36:58,480
Excessive eagerness to help

695
00:36:58,760 --> 00:37:00,220
means you're up to no good.

696
00:37:01,070 --> 00:37:01,760
Your Highness,

697
00:37:01,760 --> 00:37:03,020
let me taste it for you.

698
00:37:03,400 --> 00:37:04,190
No!

699
00:37:05,150 --> 00:37:06,360
You can't drink it.

700
00:37:06,360 --> 00:37:07,320
It's such expensive medicine.

701
00:37:07,320 --> 00:37:08,820
How can you drink it?

702
00:37:09,030 --> 00:37:10,030
You're too young.

703
00:37:10,550 --> 00:37:11,440
This medicine

704
00:37:12,070 --> 00:37:13,470
is only for His Highness.

705
00:37:15,320 --> 00:37:16,180
Your Highness,

706
00:37:16,670 --> 00:37:17,710
let me

707
00:37:18,070 --> 00:37:19,670
help you take your medicine.

708
00:37:23,710 --> 00:37:24,510
Alright.

709
00:37:28,920 --> 00:37:29,710
Come,

710
00:37:30,480 --> 00:37:31,410
open your mouth.

711
00:37:32,800 --> 00:37:34,480
You're too far. I can't reach.

712
00:37:36,550 --> 00:37:37,820
Come, be a good boy.

713
00:37:38,110 --> 00:37:39,240
Open your mouth.

714
00:37:40,680 --> 00:37:41,790
Still can't reach.

715
00:37:43,360 --> 00:37:44,150
Come closer.

716
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:51,740
Your Highness,

717
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:53,280
please take your medicine.

718
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:54,110
Wait.

719
00:37:55,110 --> 00:37:56,170
Sit here to feed me.

720
00:37:57,070 --> 00:37:57,880
Sit?

721
00:37:59,300 --> 00:38:00,060
Sit?

722
00:38:03,960 --> 00:38:05,420
Is this really necessary?

723
00:38:05,440 --> 00:38:06,670
Whether it's necessary or not

724
00:38:06,670 --> 00:38:07,400
depends on how badly

725
00:38:07,400 --> 00:38:09,590
you want me to take this medicine.

726
00:38:13,150 --> 00:38:13,960
Fine!

727
00:38:17,880 --> 00:38:19,360
Then I'll sit here

728
00:38:19,390 --> 00:38:21,320
and feed you your medicine slowly.

729
00:38:33,360 --> 00:38:34,850
Come on, Your Highness.

730
00:38:35,480 --> 00:38:37,190
Can you drink it now?

731
00:38:40,960 --> 00:38:42,690
You're still not close enough.

732
00:38:45,960 --> 00:38:46,820
Your Highness,

733
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:49,800
aren't you afraid I might

734
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:52,400
shove this spoon right down your throat?

735
00:38:53,670 --> 00:38:54,730
You wouldn't dare.

736
00:38:55,920 --> 00:38:56,710
Fine then.

737
00:38:57,760 --> 00:38:59,590
Let's see

738
00:38:59,800 --> 00:39:01,480
whether I dare or not.

739
00:39:02,320 --> 00:39:03,110
Come on, be good,

740
00:39:03,110 --> 00:39:04,040
open your mouth.

741
00:39:05,510 --> 00:39:06,840
Is this close enough?

742
00:39:07,550 --> 00:39:08,480
Close enough?

743
00:39:09,070 --> 00:39:09,880
Here,

744
00:39:10,070 --> 00:39:12,030
time for your medicine.

745
00:39:12,030 --> 00:39:12,760
I...

746
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:13,960
Come on.

747
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:20,150
I'm sorry,

748
00:39:20,400 --> 00:39:21,330
my foot slipped.

749
00:39:22,550 --> 00:39:24,550
You did that on purpose, didn't you?

750
00:39:28,480 --> 00:39:29,280
What...

751
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:30,340
What are you doing?

752
00:39:30,550 --> 00:39:33,280
Next time you want to throw yourself
into my arms,

753
00:39:33,400 --> 00:39:34,190
remember to

754
00:39:35,150 --> 00:39:36,510
dress more elegantly.

755
00:39:37,070 --> 00:39:37,590
I...

756
00:39:54,930 --> 00:39:56,350
Take it easy.

757
00:40:02,060 --> 00:40:04,860
Miss Song Yiting showed me
nothing but sincerity,

758
00:40:05,800 --> 00:40:08,330
yet I threw her genuine feelings
on the ground

759
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:10,700
and trampled on them carelessly.

760
00:40:11,000 --> 00:40:13,600
Even the wickedest person
in the martial world

761
00:40:14,710 --> 00:40:16,400
couldn't be worse than me.

762
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:18,620
Shangguan,

763
00:40:19,110 --> 00:40:20,440
don't think too much.

764
00:40:20,670 --> 00:40:22,280
You were just doing your job.

765
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:23,280
You didn't want to do that,

766
00:40:23,280 --> 00:40:24,000
right?

767
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:25,150
Tomorrow

768
00:40:25,590 --> 00:40:26,800
is the last day.

769
00:40:27,030 --> 00:40:27,840
Get

770
00:40:28,230 --> 00:40:29,190
the sword back.

771
00:40:29,590 --> 00:40:30,400
Never

772
00:40:30,840 --> 00:40:31,710
see her again.

773
00:40:33,110 --> 00:40:34,570
That's right, Shangguan.

774
00:40:34,670 --> 00:40:36,550
You can't be blamed for being harsh.

775
00:40:36,550 --> 00:40:37,710
You rejected her so clearly,

776
00:40:37,710 --> 00:40:39,570
yet she still kept pestering you.

777
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:40,590
After all,

778
00:40:40,610 --> 00:40:42,880
it's just feelings from a brief encounter.

779
00:40:42,880 --> 00:40:44,110
How deep can it really be?

780
00:40:44,110 --> 00:40:45,070
She'll most likely

781
00:40:45,070 --> 00:40:46,550
forget all about it after a while.

782
00:40:46,550 --> 00:40:47,230
-Yes.
-Yes.

783
00:40:47,230 --> 00:40:47,670
-Yes.
-Yes.

784
00:40:47,670 --> 00:40:49,280
She's not like me.

785
00:40:50,110 --> 00:40:50,920
Shangguan,

786
00:40:51,030 --> 00:40:51,960
tell me,

787
00:40:52,110 --> 00:40:53,770
if you had met Miss Song Yiting

788
00:40:53,800 --> 00:40:54,760
at a different time,

789
00:40:54,760 --> 00:40:56,030
in a different place,

790
00:40:56,150 --> 00:40:57,550
would you have fallen for

791
00:40:57,550 --> 00:40:58,590
a girl like her?

792
00:41:05,670 --> 00:41:08,590
She's in love with the fake Li Shiliu.

793
00:41:09,550 --> 00:41:10,930
A person like me

794
00:41:11,320 --> 00:41:13,070
will never get married.

795
00:41:14,230 --> 00:41:16,430
Some relationships are not meant to be,

796
00:41:16,670 --> 00:41:17,950
so some questions

797
00:41:18,710 --> 00:41:20,000
should never be asked.

798
00:41:24,400 --> 00:41:25,440
What a shame.

799
00:41:28,320 --> 00:41:29,110
Guys,

800
00:41:29,440 --> 00:41:30,710
do you think the Waning River Crescent

801
00:41:30,710 --> 00:41:32,070
has bad feng shui?

802
00:41:33,510 --> 00:41:35,040
Our Chief Master is single,

803
00:41:35,150 --> 00:41:36,680
and so is our Second Master.

804
00:41:37,670 --> 00:41:38,440
If you ask me,

805
00:41:38,440 --> 00:41:40,030
we might as well become monks,

806
00:41:40,030 --> 00:41:41,960
instead of looking for some sword.

807
00:41:42,710 --> 00:41:43,510
So,

808
00:41:44,030 --> 00:41:44,960
you lost the sword?

